name: Colourful Counting 1
description:
Wall Art for Children by Hello Yellow.

Illustration Title: Colourful Counting 1
Collection Title: Colour

'Colour' is the 5th collection by Australian design company Hello Yellow. Inspired by a love of Scandinavian design and playful colour combinations this collection is equally amazing in a nursery or kids room, or pretty much any room in the house.

Colourful Counting 1 is a high quality digital print of an original painting by Hello Yellow and has been printed on recycled Linen 280gsm paper.

Features:

- High quality digital print 
- Recycled Linen 280gsm paper
- A3 size 
- Limited edition - each print comes hand numbered and signed by the artist
- Fits perfectly into Ikea RIBBA frame for a quick and easy framing option
- Designed and made in Australia by Hello Yellow
- Free shipping worldwide
